{"id":364780,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/10/bbc｜香港「佔中」第九天-僵持局面仍持續/","date":"2014-10-06T03:56:58Z","modified":"2014-10-06T17:51:08Z","title":"BBC｜香港「佔中」第九天 僵持局面仍持續","content":"<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006014438_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\"><img class=\"align none size-full wp-image-364781\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006014438_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\" alt=\"141006014438_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese\" width=\"590\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006014438_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg 590w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006014438_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></a>在旺角，繼續有「佔中」抗議者留守街頭 （BBC中文網記者蕭爾拍攝）</p>\n<p>香港「佔領中環」行動星期一（10月6日）進入第9天，「佔中」抗議現場早晨相對平靜。</p>\n<p>BBC中文網記者蕭爾在港島金鐘附近報道，一些示威者仍然留守在金鐘海富中心通往政府總部天橋下的幹諾道中東西行車線馬路上。</p>\n<p>烈日當頭，有示威者躲在寫有「撐」字的雨傘下，躺在馬路中央，有的在馬路兩旁的帳篷裏休息。有示威者表示，他們將留守下去。</p>\n<p>早些時候，蕭爾在旺角抗議現場看到，仍有一些學生在留守。</p>\n<p>他說，一些人躺在路上休息，也有部分路過的市民與示威者爭執。現場還聚集了一些圍觀者，有媒體記者在一旁。</p>\n<p>蕭爾說，在十字路口路段上有少許警察，目前的情況相對平靜。</p>\n<p>他表示，沒有看有跡象顯示學生會撤走，也沒有看到警方有清場的跡象。</p>\n<p>以下是蕭爾在金鐘現場拍攝的照片</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006030211_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-364782\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006030211_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\" alt=\"141006030211_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese\" width=\"590\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006030211_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg 590w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006030211_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006030314_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-364783\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006030314_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\" alt=\"141006030314_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese\" width=\"590\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006030314_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg 590w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006030314_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006030406_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-364784\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006030406_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\" alt=\"141006030406_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese\" width=\"590\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006030406_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg 590w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141006030406_hk_admiralty_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></a></p>\n<p>以下是蕭爾在旺角現場拍攝的照片</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014540_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-364785\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014540_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\" alt=\"0141006014540_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese\" width=\"590\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014540_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg 590w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014540_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014634_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-364786\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014634_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\" alt=\"0141006014634_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese\" width=\"590\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014634_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg 590w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014634_hk_mongkok_protest_640x360_bbcchinese-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014755_hk_mongkok_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-364787\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014755_hk_mongkok_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg\" alt=\"0141006014755_hk_mongkok_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese\" width=\"590\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014755_hk_mongkok_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese.jpg 590w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014755_hk_mongkok_protest_scene_640x360_bbcchinese-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014850_hong_kong_mongkok_protest_624x351_bbcchinese.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-364788\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014850_hong_kong_mongkok_protest_624x351_bbcchinese.jpg\" alt=\"0141006014850_hong_kong_mongkok_protest_624x351_bbcchinese\" width=\"590\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014850_hong_kong_mongkok_protest_624x351_bbcchinese.jpg 590w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/0141006014850_hong_kong_mongkok_protest_624x351_bbcchinese-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></a></p>\n<p>在香港島的金鐘特區政府總部附近，一些抗議者凖備離開去上班，另一些人繼續留守，而警方則繼續與抗議者保持一定距離。</p>\n<p>他們讓開政府總部外的通道，以便政府雇員可以上班。</p>\n<p>《南華早報》報道，大約20名抗議者等在特首梁振英辦公室外。</p>\n<p>「佔中」支持者與政府就談判問題仍處在僵局中。</p>\n<p>香港電台報道，學聯與政府就政改對話舉行首次籌備會議。學聯說，雙方未能就3項原則達成共識，未能展開對話或談判。</p>\n<p>有留守多日的學生認為，要等到政府有誠意對話，才會離開。</p>\n<p>警方對是否會採取武力清場，沒有正面回應，但說有信心和決心讓市民回復正常生活。</p>\n<p>香港教育局宣佈香港島中西區和灣仔中學今天復課，小學、幼稚園和特殊學校則視乎中學復課後情況而再安排。<br />\n（撰稿/責編：董樂）</p>\n","author":996,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,8779],"tags":[25381,25921,8712]}